overview: Mandy Muse stole the team's playbook and now the coach and his players are out for revenge!  Jayden Black will fuck you, but only if you'll dominate that sweet ass!  Martini Bows learns that a life of crime may not have been the best choice!  Arya Faye is a bad neighbor & ends up paying the price for her rudeness!
title: Disciplined Teens 12
